2026-03-03 13:24:17,016 {"event": "http.agent_io.llm.request", "method": "POST", "url": "http://127.0.0.1:8888/v1/chat/completions", "session_id": "sess-1", "request_content_type": "application/json", "request_body": "{\"model\": \"\", \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"你是租房Agent意图解析器。请把输入解析为严格JSON，不要输出任何额外文字或Markdown。\\nintent可选值：chat/search/compare/amenities/house_detail/listings/rent/terminate/offline。\\n你必须基于可用API工具目录判断本轮最匹配的operationId，并抽取调用参数。\\n严格反幻觉：不允许编造 house_id、listing_platform、地标ID 或未提供的硬约束。\\n若用户文本里显式出现 house_id（如 HF_67），必须使用该 house_id，不得被上下文覆盖。\\n仅当用户未显式给出 house_id 且出现“这套/第一套/最开始那套”时，才可使用 context_facts 中的 focus_house_id 或 latest_search_house_ids。\\n若必填参数未知，不要猜测，保留为空并降低confidence。\\n只返回如下结构：{\\\"intent\\\":\\\"search\\\",\\\"tool_plan\\\":{\\\"operationId\\\":\\\"get_houses_by_platform\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{}},\\\"hard\\\":{},\\\"soft\\\":{},\\\"confidence\\\":0.0}。\\noperationId必须从工具目录中选择；若是纯闲聊可填 none。\\nhard可含字段：district,area,community,landmark_id,landmark_name,landmark_category,budget_min,budget_max,rent_type,layout,area_min,max_subway_dist,max_commute_min,utilities_type,move_in_date,listing_platform,house_id。\\nsoft可含字段：decoration,elevator,orientation,noise_preference,amenities,value_for_money,prioritize_subway_distance。\\ntool_plan.arguments请使用API参数名（如 max_price/rental_type/listing_platform/house_id）。\\ntool_plan.arguments必须遵守argdefs中的参数类型(type)和必填(required)，不要返回未定义参数。\\n未提及字段不要猜测，可以不返回或设为null。\\n工具目录:\\nget_landmarks|GET /api/landmarks|intent=search|required=-|params=category,district|argdefs=category:string@query;district:string@query|outputs=id,name,category,district,latitude,longitude|hints=列出地标，可按类别和行政区过滤。\\nget_landmark_by_name|GET /api/landmarks/name/{name}|intent=search|required=name|params=name|argdefs=name:string!@path(地标名称，如 西二旗站、国贸)|outputs=id,name,category,district,latitude,longitude|hints=按地标名称精确查询，适合 nearby 前置解析。\\nsearch_landmarks|GET /api/landmarks/search|intent=search|required=q|params=q,category,district|argdefs=q:string!@query(搜索关键词，必填);category:string@query;district:string@query|outputs=id,name,category,district,latitude,longitude|hints=地标模糊搜索。\\nget_landmark_by_id|GET /api/landmarks/{id}|intent=search|required=id|params=id|argdefs=id:string!@path(地标 ID，如 SS_001...)|outputs=id,name,category,district,latitude,longitude|hints=按地标 ID 查询详情。\\nget_landmark_stats|GET /api/landmarks/stats|intent=search|required=-|params=-|argdefs=-|outputs=total,by_category,by_district|hints=地标统计，不用于具体找房。\\nget_house_by_id|GET /api/houses/{house_id}|intent=house_detail|required=house_id|params=house_id|argdefs=house_id:string!@path(房源 ID，如 HF_200...)|outputs=house_id,listing_platform,rent,layout,area,district,community,subway_distance,commute_to_xierqi_min,status,tags,decoration,elevator,orientation,available_date|hints=单套房源详情。\\nget_house_listings|GET /api/houses/listings/{house_id}|intent=listings|required=house_id|params=house_id|argdefs=house_id:string!@path(房源 ID，如 HF_200...)|outputs=total,page_size,items[].listing_platform,items[].rent,items[].status,items[].url|hints=同一房源在多平台挂牌价格/状态查询。\\nget_houses_by_community|GET /api/houses/by_community|intent=search|required=community|params=community,listing_platform,page,page_size|argdefs=community:string!@query(小区名，与数据一致，如 建清...);listing_platform:string@query=链家/安居客/58同城;page:integer@query;page_size:integer@query|outputs=total,page_size,items[].house_id,items[].listing_platform,items[].rent,items[].layout,items[].district,items[].community,items[].subway_distance,items[].status|hints=给定小区名时优先。\\nget_houses_by_platform|GET /api/houses/by_platform|intent=search|required=-|params=listing_platform,district,area,min_price,max_price,bedrooms,rental_type,decoration,orientation,elevator,min_area,max_area,property_type,subway_line,max_subway_dist,subway_station,utilities_type,available_from_before,commute_to_xierqi_max,sort_by,sort_order,page,page_size|argdefs=listing_platform:string@query=链家/安居客/58同城;district:string@query;area:string@query;min_price:integer@query;max_price:integer@query;bedrooms:string@query;rental_type:string@query;decoration:string@query;orientation:string@query;elevator:string@query;min_area:integer@query;max_area:integer@query;property_type:string@query;subway_line:string@query;max_subway_dist:integer@query;subway_station:string@query;utilities_type:string@query;available_from_before:string@query;commute_to_xierqi_max:integer@query;sort_by:string@query;sort_order:string@query;page:integer@query;page_size:integer@query|outputs=total,page_size,items[].house_id,items[].listing_platform,items[].rent,items[].layout,items[].area,items[].district,items[].community,items[].subway_distance,items[].commute_to_xierqi_min,items[].status,items[].utilities_type|hints=泛化找房主入口；默认安居客。\\nget_nearby_landmarks|GET /api/houses/nearby_landmarks|intent=amenities|required=community|params=community,type,max_distance_m|argdefs=community:string!@query(小区名，用于定位基准点);type:string@query;max_distance_m:number@query|outputs=items[].name,items[].category,items[].distance_m|hints=查询小区周边商超/公园。\\nget_houses_nearby|GET /api/houses/nearby|intent=search|required=landmark_id|params=landmark_id,max_distance,listing_platform,page,page_size|argdefs=landmark_id:string!@query(地标 ID 或地标名称（支持...);max_distance:number@query;listing_platform:string@query=链家/安居客/58同城;page:integer@query;page_size:integer@query|outputs=total,page_size,items[].house_id,items[].listing_platform,items[].rent,items[].layout,items[].district,items[].community,items[].distance_to_landmark,items[].walking_distance,items[].walking_duration,items[].status|hints=按地标半径找房。\\nget_house_stats|GET /api/houses/stats|intent=search|required=-|params=-|argdefs=-|outputs=total,by_status,by_district,by_layout,price_ranges|hints=房源统计，不用于具体单房操作。\\nrent_house|POST /api/houses/{house_id}/rent|intent=rent|required=house_id,listing_platform|params=house_id,listing_platform|argdefs=house_id:string!@path(房源 ID，如 HF_200...);listing_platform:string!@query=链家/安居客/58同城(必填。明确租赁哪个平台；三平...)|outputs=house_id,listing_platform,status,message|hints=办理租房，必须指定平台。\\nterminate_rental|POST /api/houses/{house_id}/terminate|intent=terminate|required=house_id,listing_platform|params=house_id,listing_platform|argdefs=house_id:string!@path(房源 ID，如 HF_200...);listing_platform:string!@query=链家/安居客/58同城(必填。明确操作哪个平台；三平...)|outputs=house_id,listing_platform,status,message|hints=办理退租，必须指定平台。\\ntake_offline|POST /api/houses/{house_id}/offline|intent=offline|required=house_id,listing_platform|params=house_id,listing_platform|argdefs=house_id:string!@path(房源 ID，如 HF_200...);listing_platform:string!@query=链家/安居客/58同城(必填。明确操作哪个平台；三平...)|outputs=house_id,listing_platform,status,message|hints=办理下架，必须指定平台。\\nenums|listing_platform=链家,安居客,58同城;rental_type=整租,合租;landmark_category=subway,company,landmark;nearby_type=shopping,park;sort_by=price,area,subway;sort_order=asc,desc\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"{\\\"history_summary\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"context_facts\\\": {}, \\\"message\\\": \\\"帮我找房\\\"}\"}], \"max_tokens\": 256, \"stream\": false}"}
